thread.title: Brian Bosworth

author: Brian Bosworth
title: Brian Bosworth
text: My wife and I rented a small car for a few days during a rush trip to Melbourne. You almost expect poor service when the price is so low. This was not the case and both the car and the service were top class. We were picked up within minutes of calling and from the young fellow who picked us up to the bloke who took the car off us at the end the staff were very efficient and friendly. We have used airport rentals before and will not hesitate to use them again any time we need a car.
